{"tid":1409554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保護好自己，唔好再亂屌人影相","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:22:15.000Z","uid":179014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c182220c19898d389c7f1f25e8ca643f2b1fe0","tid":1409554,"uid":179014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:25:35.000Z","msg":"就算市民唔影，記者一定會影。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">無人影住一陣間俾狗打，邊個搵番啲相同片出黎？無相同片既話文宣組點樣支持個活動？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就算唔係前線，都麻煩大家戴番個口罩，最好包條頭巾/戴副反光太陽眼鏡 (要淺色，否則入夜會太黑睇唔到野)。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重點係，真係好多平民百姓純粹出於好奇咁影下相，係一個難得既機會俾啲平時唔關心政治既人睇下依家發生咩事。呢一刻無啦啦屌走人，真係唔係咁好。自己保護好自己，先係上策。"},{"pid":"ea3068f120b76f877d9c6da2785260bf8197ea17","tid":1409554,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:27:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc0ee595d318a037214c4ac6faaf6096d29ff71d","tid":1409554,"uid":179014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e110943b344db64739dd3b7ce5dd9189d8e3cef","tid":1409554,"uid":179014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"743e36ccf1009f371ed8e35cfc8d74b2bab9e7b1","tid":1409554,"uid":179014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}